        "title": "Power Schools",
        "excerpt": "Fighter                 Name       Description                             Acrobat              You dodge and weave across the battlefield, moving with incredible speed                             Berserker              You smash enemies with aggressive bursts of murderous rage                             Cyborg              You replace your biological body parts with advanced metal cybernetics                             Duelist              You parry enemy attacks and respond with well-timed ripostes               Sharpshooter                 Name       Description                             Demolitionist              You destroy buildings and people alike with a variety of powerful explosives                             Hunter              You fire with care and precision to take out enemies at incredible distances                             Juggernaut              You mow down the opposition with heavy machine guns or explosives                             Rogue              You chance your way into victory, consistently getting lucky hits or dodges               Expert                 Name       Description                             Battlesmith              You wear a suit of advanced power armor that protects you from harm                             Gadgeteer              You invent novel technological devices for a variety of purposes                             Mastermind              You support your party both in and out of battle, with a plan for every situation                             Roboticist              You control numerous robotic drones, customizing them for any situation               Sorcerer                 Name       Description                             Blaster              You blast enemies away with devastating evocations of elemental energy                             Fundamentalist              You manipulate the fundamental laws of reality to control space, time, and magic                             Healer              You heal your allies and poison your enemies with body-affecting magic                             Psion              You specialize in mental magic that affects other creatures' thoughts or actions               Adept                 Name       Description                             Champion              You manifest your belief in a cause as divine blessings on the battlefield                             Diviner              You predict the future, see distant events, and track creatures with magic                             Shapeshifter              You transform yourself or other creatures into animals or monsters                             Telekinetic              You move objects with your mind to protect yourself or hurl boulders at foes               Conjurer                 Name       Description                             Druid              You command the spirits of nature, manipulating wild animals and plants                             Elementalist              You harness elemental spirits to precisely control the natural world                             Necromancer              You channel necrotic energy to slay the living, then raise the spirits of the dead                             Sage              You employ intelligent spirits to gather information and perform tasks",
